appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
1. Extended selection of the number of wins in the set.
2. Option “Hide Scores” has been added to “27”, “Scores”, “Sector” and “DDV”.
3. Added the ability to select bots of different levels in a x01 pair game.
4. For single player game in “180 Around the Clock”, “27”, “Scores” and “Sector” the mode “Game with shadow” is added (against best or last result).
5. Added the ability to sort games by date (statistics).
6. Fixed bugs.
